{"tid":306283,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一樣唔知點解自己細個會驚既野","createTime":"2017-07-02T11:42:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-03T00:58:43.000Z","uid":60796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fb19caf4b28ed933a103592db6af518270b05b48","tid":306283,"uid":60796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T11:42:38.000Z","msg":"我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n細個屋企有啲兒歌DVD, 呀媽會播比我睇<br />\n隻碟既片頭有個間公司既logo(隻豹)跑出黎,咬住隻碟<br />\n我細個驚到一擺完隻碟入去,就即刻要衝入房<br />\n等片頭完左先出番廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好on9 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/02/193856_b1625ccf58e77aaf0342b88cb0c87bea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F02%2F193856_b1625ccf58e77aaf0342b88cb0c87bea.jpg&h=3aee5a32&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e08842b0c81b029b02f90a767fd2c6adacbe0840","tid":306283,"uid":64308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T11:44:52.000Z","msg":"夜晚街邊既樹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccd3f025d75d0c6b2a0e545e33d415d60bcfc96d","tid":306283,"uid":60796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T12:18:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>夜晚街邊既樹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n朝早就唔驚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"940482de283303868fdaf8a75db917c3b4dd1b5f","tid":306283,"uid":13657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T12:23:55.000Z","msg":"好驚啲衫紐"},{"pid":"b4d028bfd8daf192791081e6b83996ab04772a79","tid":306283,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T12:24:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10d696cc10dec29b42598509af1432ac09be4c7e","tid":306283,"uid":13657,"like":0,"disl